I am excited to share my cars on Turo!

I love beautiful, well-engineered cars and enjoy sharing the beauty and performance of my Porsche 911 (Carrera S manual transmission and Carrera GTS Cabriolet PDK), Lucid Air Dream Edition, Audi Q7, and Tesla Model 3 with lovers of great cars.

-----


Je suis un passionné de l'automobile, de son histoire, son design et ses performances.

Je suis ravi de partager mes voitures sur Turo, une Porsche 911S de 2006, une 911 GTS cabriolet de 2015, la Lucid Air Dream Edition, une Audi Q7 et une Tesla Model 3 avec les passionnés de l'auto

I've been featured on Bloomberg TV. 
Check it out:
https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2017-05-26/the-sharing-economy-s-entrepreneurial-ecosystems-video

Welcome to the wonderful Bay Area. I'm here to help with your travel and hospitality needs.
Im originally from Ireland, living in the Bay area since 2009. I love the diversity and opportunity of the Bay area. The home of hi-tech innovation and the birthplace of the sharing economy.  
So please let me share my cars with you to make your visit as enjoyable as possible. 

Some extra items I am willing to rent to you for $5 per day each item:
a 2 person tent
1 adult size sleeping pad
A camping stove ( you must supply your own butane gas)
1 camping chair
A hand cart for moving boxes, max weight 150 lbs.
Visit my Facebook page. 
Like and leave a review here:
Www.facebook.com/RentFromALocal


For an instant on demand ride use  Uber and Lyft. First time users get a free ride with these promo codes.
Uber: ANNC420. 
Lyft: ANN620


Thank you for renting. Please drive safe and enjoy your time here in the Bay area.

Ann

"We like black wheels and we cannot lie!"

Founded in 2021 by two friends and auto enthusiasts, BWB offers well-maintained, fun-to-drive vehicles in the San Francisco Bay Area to guests who live locally or are visiting this beautiful region of the country.  Rent one of our vehicles on Turo today!

As our name suggests, most of the cars we feature are outfitted with BLACK wheels so you can arrive in style, wherever you may be headed.

www.BlackWheeledBeauties.com
https://www.instagram.com/blackwheeledbeauties/
Top Review in the Bay Area
Safe, defensive driver. It’s not a race, it’s just a road.

Cars are much more than just tools or objects, they allow us to travel to new places, visit our loved ones, create meaningful memories, tell great stories, and ultimately help us fulfill our goals and dreams. 

As an All-Star-Host, being able to share our cars with guests to help them create their own stories means the world to us.

As an entrepreneur with multiple businesses, a mom who loves to travel and values doing so in comfort and luxury, I want to offer an efficient, memorable and unique experience to those who book with me. I understand and value exceptional customer experiences. As a Turo guest, you book for convenience, vehicle selection and a personal touch. It’s my goal to provide all those factors and go beyond your expectations where possible. I am communicative, outgoing and helpful. I personalize every guest experience with a welcome gift at check in, tips and guides on travel destinations if requested and a pristine car. My husband and I love traveling overseas as well as roadtripping around the US. We understand the importance of a reliable and well equipped vehicle to get you to point A and B and all the stops in between. With numerous add on features you can travel alone, with your significant other or family in luxury and style. Check out my other vehicles and follow me on Instagram @Lotus7enterprises to see our newest cars as we grow our fleet.
